sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Administrator
    participant UI as Frontend UI
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Job as Job Controller
    participant Worker as Netmiko Worker
    participant Device as Network Device
    participant FS as File System
    participant DB as Database
    
    Admin->>UI: Buka menu Jobs
    UI->>API: Request daftar job
    API->>DB: Ambil data job
    DB-->>API: Return jobs list
    API-->>UI: Return jobs data
    UI->>Admin: Tampilkan job status & history
    
    Admin->>UI: Klik Run Manual Backup
    UI->>API: Request jalankan backup
    API->>Job: Buat job baru
    Job->>DB: Simpan job record
    DB-->>Job: Job created
    
    loop Untuk setiap device aktif
        Job->>Worker: Fetch konfigurasi device
        Worker->>Device: Koneksi ke device
        Device-->>Worker: Koneksi berhasil
        Worker->>Device: Ambil konfigurasi
        Device-->>Worker: Return konfigurasi
        Worker->>FS: Simpan ke file
        FS-->>Worker: File tersimpan
        Worker->>DB: Simpan record backup
        DB-->>Worker: Backup tercatat
    end
    
    Job->>DB: Update status job
    API-->>UI: Return job selesai
    UI->>Admin: Tampilkan eksekusi selesai
    
    Admin->>UI: Buka menu Backups
    UI->>API: Request daftar backup
    API->>DB: Ambil data backup
    DB-->>API: Return backup list
    API-->>UI: Return backups data
    UI->>Admin: Tampilkan list backup dengan detail
    
    alt Preview Backup
        Admin->>UI: Klik Preview
        UI->>API: Request isi backup
        API->>FS: Baca file backup
        FS-->>API: Return isi file
        API-->>UI: Return konten konfigurasi
        UI->>Admin: Tampilkan preview isi konfigurasi
    else Download Backup
        Admin->>UI: Klik Download
        UI->>API: Request download file
        API->>FS: Baca file backup
        FS-->>API: Return file stream
        API-->>UI: Return file stream
        UI->>Admin: Download file konfigurasi
    end
